00:27:04,080 --> 00:27:05,120
 Yes, of Gentiles too.

505
00:27:05,120 --> 00:27:07,760
 So there's only one God who will justify

506
00:27:07,760 --> 00:27:09,320
 the circumcised, the Jewish people,

507
00:27:09,320 --> 00:27:11,280
 by faith and the uncircumcised,

508
00:27:11,280 --> 00:27:13,480
 the Gentiles, through that same faith.

509
00:27:14,600 --> 00:27:18,600
 This is how they can be saved from their sin,

510
00:27:18,600 --> 00:27:21,080
 by faith in Jesus.

511
00:27:21,080 --> 00:27:25,280
 Which is, well,

512
00:27:25,280 --> 00:27:32,240
 3.2 billion people living with all kinds of ideas

513
00:27:32,240 --> 00:27:33,240
 of how to get to God.

514
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:34,520
 I think about, I think about standing

515
00:27:34,520 --> 00:27:39,120
 in one of those red areas, outside a temple.

516
00:27:39,120 --> 00:27:40,600
 One guy worships at that temple,

517
00:27:40,600 --> 00:27:43,140
 another guy worships at a different temple

